keywords

Examples of additionalincorrectcode for this rule with the"as-needed", { "keywords": true }options:

/*eslint quote-props: ["error", "as-needed", { "keywords": true }]*/

var x = {
    while: 1,
    volatile: "foo"
};

Examples of additionalincorrectcode for this rule with the"consistent-as-needed", { "keywords": true }options:

/*eslint quote-props: ["error", "consistent-as-needed", { "keywords": true }]*/

